HELP SCREEN --- PRESS F2 TO PLAY

Welcome to Blast Tactics, an outer-space rogue-like game in Common
Lisp.

Greetings, Contractor! Join the fight against the Droid Infestation.

Use your numeric keypad to move, or the roguelike movement keys:
   ^        
  YKU        
< H L >      1 = drop time bomb
  BJN        2 = pulse cannon
   v         3 = activate shield (if any)

To fire, hold down the CONTROL key and press any direction.
To attack with a melee weapon, hold down ALT and press any direction.
To wait in place without moving, hit W or SPACE.
To enter a location or gateway, press ENTER.
To leave most screens, move off the edge of the map,
   or press ENTER on the blue-and-white launchpad.
To quit, press CONTROL-Q.
To restart after dying, press CONTROL-PERIOD.
To highlight the player's location, press CONTROL-ESCAPE.
To enter a vehicle, press P.
To exit a vehicle, press CONTROL-P.
To examine an object, left-click on it.

For DVORAK and other key layouts, see the included INSTALL file.


